span></p><p><span>It’s a glimpse that gives a nice spread of top-tier athletes examining the hows and whys that all of us normal folk scratch our heads over.</span></p><p>You can read Canyon’s post-op interview of the rider <a href=\"https://www.canyon.com/en-us/blog-content/kokopelli-trail-fkt-peter-stetina.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.<br>Or, try to keep up with Stetina’s adventures <a href=\"https://www.peterstetina.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.</p></div></div>","author":"Mark Wilson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"e5f87eb07d175f848abf7e7724eef5757ad0c79f12e925999a99e1df9b586c7b","category":"Cycling"}